	"system": {
		"description": "<p>Your tight focus on the warrior’s discipline to the exclusion of other concerns has made you exceptional even among other warriors. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Strength, Dexterity, or Constitution increases by +1, to a maximum of 20</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with two rare weapons of your choice.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with improvised weapons.</p></li><li><p>Your exertion pool increases by 1.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with a combat tradition you are not already proficient with and a maneuver from it that you could learn. It does not count against your maneuvers known.</p></li></ul>",
